{"tid":2005644,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇鄭錦滿] 新一屆圖書館諮詢委員會任命 包括多名民建聯落選議員 鄺俊宇卸任","createTime":"2020-05-07T08:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T15:42:20.000Z","uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ab687a12d54e435df9b6d081e5c349abd88b8b","tid":2005644,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T08:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2540000/2542755/77B30D77D910492EB9054DFE070CEC1B_O_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2540000%2F2542755%2F77B30D77D910492EB9054DFE070CEC1B_O_1024.JPG&h=33bb3bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202005/07/P2020050700247.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202005%2F07%2FP2020050700247.htm&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=5da5610f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202005/07/P2020050700247.htm</a><br />\n新一屆公共圖書館諮詢委員會已獲委任，任期兩年至二○二二年四月三十日。<br />\n<br />\n  委員會就公共圖書館的發展向政府提供意見，包括圖書館設施和服務的發展策略和措施，香港中央圖書館的角色、功能和管理，以及鼓勵社會支持並與各界合作推廣閱讀風氣、終身學習和文學藝術等。<br />\n<br />\n  以下為新一屆委員會的成員名單：<br />\n<br />\n主席：   李惠光(城大副校長(行政))<br />\n副主席：  羅乃萱(家庭發展基金總幹事)<br />\n委員：陳健雄＊(小童群益會總幹事)<br />\n      陳麗霞(香港教育工作者聯會黃楚標學校助理校長)<br />\n      陳玉燕＊(風采中學校長)<br />\n      <span style=\"color: red;\">鄭泳舜＊(民建聯、立法會議員、F03南昌北落選區議員)</span><br />\n     <span style=\"color: red;\"> 張思穎(民建聯中央委員)</span><br />\n      周博軒＊(汕头市政协、駿碼科技（8490）執行主席)<br />\n      周子烈(前政府新聞處新聞主任、青年創研庫成員)<br />\n      蔡世鴻＊(中華基督教會協和小學（長沙灣）校長)<br />\n      蔡少綿＊(前環境局政治助理、港鐵事務總監)<br />\n      崔日雄教授＊(職道生涯規劃輔導協會總監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n      何蘭生(保良局李徐松聲紀念幼稚園校長)<br />\n      <span style=\"color: red;\">洪錦鉉(民建聯、J11寶達落選區議員)</span><br />\n      葉錦蓮(港大圖書館及資訊管理碩士)<br />\n      郭斯恆(理大設計學院助理教授、霓虹燈專家)<br />\n      林欣彤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n      教育局代表<br />\n      政府檔案處代表<br />\n      民政事務局代表    <br />\n      康樂及文化事務署代表<br />\n<br />\n＊新委任成員  <br />\n<br />\n民政事務局發言人感謝已卸任的九名委員（莊明蓮教授、<span style=\"color: red;\">鄺俊宇</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、林浣心、梁湘明教授、潘步釗博士、蘇家碧、譚國根教授、黃沛琳及葉潤雲）過去對委員會的支持和貢獻。"},{"pid":"dca1f211a29165344ab182528bab8ab707ca9f25","tid":2005644,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T08:44:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkpl.gov.hk/tc/about-us/intro/plac/agenda.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkpl.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout-us%2Fintro%2Fplac%2Fagenda.html&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=142e27c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkpl.gov.hk/tc/about-us/intro/plac/agenda.html</a><br />\nHK NO IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上一次會議討論摘要係<br />\n<blockquote>二零一八年十月二十六日第三十三次會議</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkpl.gov.hk/tc/common/attachments/about-us/intro/Discussion%20Summary%20for%20Meeting_33rd%20PLAC%20Meeting%20(Chinese).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkpl.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcommon%2Fattachments%2Fabout-us%2Fintro%2FDiscussion%2520Summary%2520for%2520Meeting_33rd%2520PLAC%2520Meeting%2520%28Chinese%29.pdf&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=6447ea4b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkpl.gov.hk/tc/common/attachments/about-us/intro/Discussion%20Summary%20for%20Meeting_33rd%20PLAC%20Meeting%20(Chinese).pdf</a><br />\n二 零 一 九 年 七 月 先UPLOAD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc9507f8a80aad3a5096584dbb3a1b3af0ad78f","tid":2005644,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T08:44:53.000Z","msg":"官方認證✅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pi